snippet.title: Of Gods And Men: The Daybreak Empire Trailer | Out now on Steam and itch.io!
snippet.description:
Of Gods And Men: The Daybreak Empire is out now for PC on Steam and itch.io. Our retro, story-driven, turn-based tactics game will be on sale for 40% off for the first week!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/936610/Of_Gods_and_Men_The_Daybreak_Empire/
Itch: https://deadgenre.itch.io/daybreakempire

You can also grab the soundtrack for pay what you want over on Bandcamp!
Bandcamp: https://deadgenrestudios.bandcamp.com

We also have some awesome merch you can grab at our Redbubble!
Redbubble: https://www.redbubble.com/people/deadgenre
